<br />

<br />
First attempt...
<br />

<br />
Mage AOE nukes the camp killing everything.  Well we cleared the camp didn't we?
<br />

<br />
Second attempt...
<br />

<br />
Mage accidentally targets the scout and sicks his pet on him.  Scout is dead in an instant.
<br />

<br />
(Hey this is starting to cost me money)
<br />

<br />
Third attempt...
<br />
4 and a half hours, no Officer.  Finally pack it in to try another day.
<br />

<br />
Next day - Group 50 BL, 48Pally, 52Cleric.  (Still Overkill)
<br />

<br />
Forth attempt...
<br />
2nd Wave brings an officer.  Pet solos officer while we mop up the rest of the wave.
<br />

<br />
Jenana B'Nana
