<br />
Did the GF epic battle 2 dyas ago. Just me (52 bst) and my 53 Chanter buddy. I was way too anxious and killed the scout during the first raid. After gathering myself ) we fought for what seemed to be at least a dozen waves. Scout never got below 2 bubs of health, even when I LD'd and got back on to find my Chanter friend had handled things during my 5 minute log on. Eventually The Officer spawned (I didnt even know he did...I guess I expected some giant Grimlimg or something) Buddy told me he was at my feet at the end of a wave.I got his scalp plus a couple of other goodies that would have been of alot more use had i been 45-49. Anyways...it was fun, but much too long..my nerves were shot by the end )</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
